* LMDB_NAV_APPEND_SHAKEDOWN_01.DTS
*
* Purpose:
*   Verify:
*     1) TOP / BOTTOM respect logical order
*     2) LIST starts from current logical position
*     3) SEEK lands on correct ordered record
*     4) APPEND BLANK generates SID and inserts into active order
*     5) blank LNAME sorts first
*     6) cleanup via DELETE + PACK restores table
*
* Assumptions:
*   - STUDENTS is openable
*   - STUDENTS.CDX / LMDB env exists
*   - SID and LNAME tags exist
*
* Notes:
*   - Mutates live data
*   - Appends two records
*   - Deletes them at end
*   - PACK is required for final cleanup
*
* Recommended:
*   Run on a copy if you want a pristine baseline

ECHO ON
SET TALK ON
SET DELETED ON

ECHO "===== BEGIN LMDB_NAV_APPEND_SHAKEDOWN_01 ====="

USE students
SET INDEX TO students.cdx

ECHO "===== BASELINE PHYSICAL SNAPSHOT ====="
SET ORDER TO 0
TOP
LIST 5
BOTTOM
LIST 5

ECHO "===== SID ORDER : TOP / LIST ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG SID
TOP
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== SID ORDER : BOTTOM / LIST ====="
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== SID ORDER : SEEK KNOWN VALUES ====="
SEEK 50000000
AREA
TUP
LIST 3

SEEK 50000199
AREA
TUP
LIST 3

ECHO "===== LNAME ORDER : TOP / LIST ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
TOP
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== LNAME ORDER : BOTTOM / LIST ====="
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== LNAME ORDER : SEEK KNOWN VALUES ====="
SEEK ANDERSON
AREA
TUP
LIST 5

SEEK ZZZ_ANDERSON_TEST
AREA
TUP
LIST 3

ECHO "===== APPEND BLANK UNDER SID ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG SID
BOTTOM
AREA
APPEND BLANK
AREA
DISPLAY
TUP

ECHO "===== VERIFY GENERATED SID UNDER SID TAG ====="
SEEK 50000200
AREA
DISPLAY
LIST 3

ECHO "===== FILL NEW SID-ORDER RECORD ====="
REPLACE lname WITH "ZZZ_NAV_TEST_1"
REPLACE fname WITH "Alpha"
REPLACE gender WITH "X"
REPLACE major WITH "CSCI"
REPLACE gpa WITH "4.00"
DISPLAY
TUP

ECHO "===== VERIFY SEEK + POSITION AFTER FILL ====="
SEEK 50000200
AREA
LIST 3

ECHO "===== VERIFY LNAME ORDER SEES NEW ROW ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
SEEK ZZZ_NAV_TEST_1
AREA
DISPLAY
LIST 3
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== APPEND BLANK UNDER LNAME ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
TOP
AREA
APPEND BLANK
AREA
DISPLAY
TUP

ECHO "===== VERIFY BLANK LNAME SORTS FIRST ====="
TOP
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== VERIFY GENERATED SID FOR SECOND APPEND ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG SID
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== FILL SECOND APPENDED RECORD ====="
REPLACE lname WITH "AAA_NAV_TEST_2"
REPLACE fname WITH "Beta"
REPLACE gender WITH "M"
REPLACE major WITH "MATH"
REPLACE gpa WITH "3.50"
DISPLAY
TUP

ECHO "===== VERIFY SECOND RECORD BY LNAME ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
SEEK AAA_NAV_TEST_2
AREA
DISPLAY
LIST 5

ECHO "===== VERIFY TOP/BOTTOM STILL WORK AFTER BOTH APPENDS ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG SID
TOP
AREA
LIST 5
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
TOP
AREA
LIST 5
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== DELETE APPENDED TEST ROWS ====="
SET ORDER TO TAG SID
SEEK 50000200
AREA
DELETE
DISPLAY

BOTTOM
AREA
DELETE
DISPLAY

ECHO "===== VERIFY DELETED HIDDEN ====="
TOP
LIST 5
BOTTOM
LIST 5

ECHO "===== VERIFY DELETED VISIBLE ====="
LIST ALL

ECHO "===== PACK CLEANUP ====="
PACK

ECHO "===== FINAL VERIFICATION AFTER PACK ====="
USE students
SET INDEX TO students.cdx

SET ORDER TO TAG SID
TOP
AREA
LIST 5
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
TOP
AREA
LIST 5
BOTTOM
AREA
LIST 5

ECHO "===== END LMDB_NAV_APPEND_SHAKEDOWN_01 ====="